- Past tense strong action verb + specific action + tech or method + result or impact
- Keep bullets to 1-2 lines. Use white space for scannability.
- Vary language across bullets - never repeat the exact same phrase.
- Focus detail on the most recent and relevant roles. Use fewer bullets for older or less relevant work.
- Best bullet formula: action verb + what was built, improved, or delivered + tools or context + result
